   controlled trials from inception to April 2023. Two reviewers critically
   and independently assessed the risk of bias using Cochrane Collaboration
   criteria and extracted correlated data using the designed form. All
   analyses were performed with Review Manager 5.3.
   Results: Ten studies were included in the systematic review, with a
   total of 830 patients (FTS group: 415; control group: 415). The results
