   interferedneurotransmitter contents, and transcription of
   neurodevelopment-relatedgenes in zebrafish larvae. Metabolomics analysis
   revealed changesof metabolites primarily involved in glycolipid
   metabolism, oxidativephosphorylation, and oxidative stress, which were
   validated throughthe alterations of multiple biomarkers at various
