   difference in metamorphopsia between gas and silicon oil (SO) in the PPV
   group (RR = 0.89, 95\% CI: 0.69 to 1.13).ConclusionThe incidence of
   postoperative metamorphopsia is higher in macular-off RRD, and PFCL
