   technologies in metabolomics. In addition, we reviewed recent
   applications of MS-based metabolomics for the inves-tigation of toxic
   effects of xenobiotics on microbial and host metabolism. It was
   demonstrated that metabolomics, gut microbiome profiling, and their
   combination have a high potential to identify metabolic and microbial
   markers of xenobiotic exposure and determine its mechanism. Further,
